@startuml
title Selective reading of a statechart diagram

[*] --> Ordered : «M» Plane Ordered/

state Ordered
state "In Maintenance" as InMaintenance
state "Ready for Use" as ReadyForUse
state "Scheduled for Maintenance" as ScheduledForMaintenance

Ordered --> InMaintenance : «M» Plane Delivered/
InMaintenance --> ReadyForUse : «M» Plane Available/
ReadyForUse --> InMaintenance : «M» Plane not Available/

ReadyForUse : «M» Assign Plane/
ReadyForUse : «M» Complete Flight/

ReadyForUse --> ScheduledForMaintenance : «M» Scheduling Plane\nfor Maintenance
ScheduledForMaintenance --> ReadyForUse : «M» Complete Flight [More Flights]/
ScheduledForMaintenance --> InMaintenance : «M» Complete Flight\n[No more Flights]/

InMaintenance --> [*] : «M» Plane Withdrawn/

@enduml